<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> count_unique [reuse, use_induction]:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>id c #i #j<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span><span class="hl_operator">(</span>Counter( id, c ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">∧</span> <span class="hl_operator">(</span>Counter( id, c ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span><span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">⇒</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span>#i <span class="hl_operator">=</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span>&quot;<br/>
<a class="internal-link edit" href="/thy/trace/13/main/edit/count_unique">edit lemma</a>  or  <a class="internal-link delete" href="/thy/trace/13/main/delete/count_unique">delete lemma</a></span><br/>
